    "description": {
      "es": "",
      "en": "Call func(*args), while tracing is enabled. The tracing state is saved, and restored afterwards. This is intended to be called from a debugger from a checkpoint, to recursively debug or profile some other code. Tracing is suspended while calling a tracing function set by settrace() or setprofile() to avoid infinite recursion. call_tracing() enables explicit recursion of the tracing function."
